00:04:05.961 --> 00:04:11.261
accepted Nathan's goods - not because they
were needed - but because they valued and

00:04:11.261 --> 00:04:15.911
admired his independence and his spirit.
I mean, the people that you meet who actually

00:04:15.911 --> 00:04:22.911
knew him are honored that they knew him cause
he's a legend. And if they could support him

00:04:23.130 --> 00:04:29.170
by bartering with him and honoring, I mean,
knowing that this is the greatest gift that

00:04:29.170 --> 00:04:35.531
he has to give you. Even though you don't
need this rabbit - that is - I mean, it was

00:04:35.531 --> 00:04:41.801
gold to him. 
