00:05:15.211 --> 00:05:22.211
this way. Most of us are part of the economic
and financial systems that enable trade, consumption,

00:05:23.181 --> 00:05:28.931
saving, and investing. These systems are essential
to our modern way of life. And to make best

00:05:28.931 --> 00:05:31.410
use of them we need to understand how they
work.

